      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning shape\u2014it honestly looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, keeping it garage-stored and detailed regularly. It\u2019s spotless inside and out, and I'm confident you won't find one better cared for. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' feel without the dealership headache, this is the one for you! Drop me a message if you have any questions, I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
