    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and documented rod bearing service, ensuring structural and internal longevity. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers tactile, short-throw engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut with original bushings and dampening rates preserved. Finished in flawless paint with a preserved interior, this is a turn-key specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
