    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolutely flawless 2021 Audi S5 Sportback in Daytona Gray Pearl. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained to a standard rarely seen on the secondary market, truly earning its 'mint' designation. The exterior paint is protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, offering a deep, liquid-like shine that is entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. The 19-inch 5-arm-pylon design wheels are pristine, with no curb rash or imperfections. Inside, the Magma Red Fine Nappa leather interior remains in showroom condition; the bolsters show zero wear, and the cabin still retains its original new-car scent. Every piece of carbon fiber trim and every Alcantara insert is tactilely perfect. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively at Audi dealerships ahead of schedule. All documentation, including the original window sticker and two sets of keys, are included. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that is indistinguishable from a brand-new delivery.",
      "price": 48500.0,
